<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/51831148-bryan-forsyth"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_100x100-c7bfe730633c9983e27caaa66a8e244a.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/51831148-bryan-forsyth">Bryan Forsyth</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The &apos;magic&apos; is purely in the minds of the characters. Its source is superstition, irrationality, ignorance, and religion.<br/><br/>You will not see thunderbolts<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The 'magic' is purely in the minds of the characters. Its source is superstition, irrationality, ignorance, and religion.<br /><br />You will not see thunderbolts fly from staffs or supernatural healing of deadly wounds.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
