<div id="review_492040246" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/492040246" />
    <a title="Mr. Matt" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/15984059-mr-matt"><img alt="Mr. Matt" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1401911574p2/15984059.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/492040246?book_show_action=true">Jan 01, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mr. Matt" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mr. Matt" href="/user/show/15984059-mr-matt">Mr. Matt</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/15984059-mr-matt?shelf=hf-medieval-europe">hf-medieval-europe</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer492040246" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4487875448685830872">Simply one of the best historical fiction reads out there. A unique retelling of the Arthur legend as it may have really happened. Arthur is a Celtic warlord in a post-roman Britain. Merlin is a druid, but his magic is more of he slight of hand variety. The story takes place against a ripe backdrop of change - Romano-Celts versus invading Saxons and Angles and the new Christian God against the Old Gods. Great stuff. Highly recommended.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


